784
00:46:26.008 --> 00:46:29.928
The current consensus criteria established in 2011 outlines stages

785
00:46:29.968 --> 00:46:33.548
of pre-cachexia beginning with symptoms and physiologic changes, followed by

786
00:46:33.588 --> 00:46:37.408
