788
00:46:41.197 --> 00:46:44.968
So this is inherently dynamic. But in clinical research,

789
00:46:45.508 --> 00:46:49.228
cachexia is much more typically operationalized as a static

790
00:46:49.548 --> 00:46:50.388
5%

791
00:46:51.748 --> 00:46:54.688
weight loss or greater over six months or less.

792
00:46:54.708 --> 00:46:58.408
And once a patient has reached that threshold, they're sort of considered forever

