797
00:47:13.728 --> 00:47:16.728
trajectories that have these sort of sliding six-month windows.

798
00:47:17.228 --> 00:47:21.088
And that lets us leverage the rich electronic data that are available

799
00:47:21.098 --> 00:47:24.028
to us in our healthcare system to study this.

800
00:47:24.748 --> 00:47:28.628
So when we implemented his approach in nearly 6,000 of our patients

