01:35:33.864 --> 01:35:36.384
drive the defining features, say, the negative

1618
01:35:37.604 --> 01:35:41.344
energy balance through reduced food intake, and GDF15 is one of those

1619
01:35:41.384 --> 01:35:45.164
hormones that signals to the brain to drive food aversion and negative energy

1620
01:35:45.204 --> 01:35:49.124
balance. They can be blocked, and others, not myself, and to my

1621
01:35:49.164 --> 01:35:52.644
knowledge, none of the speakers in this session have made contributions to

1622
01:35:52.684 --> 01:35:55.344
understanding that specifically, and there are clinical trials now.

1623
01:35:55.384 --> 01:35:59.024
A phase II trial was reported where GDF15

1624
01:35:59.064 --> 01:36:02.564
signaling to the brain is blocked in those patients who have high

1625
01:36:02.624 --> 01:36:06.404
GDF15, and there are suggestions that the outcome is better

1626
01:36:06.624 --> 01:36:07.264
based on

1627
01:36:08.164 --> 01:36:11.344
muscle mass, if I remember correctly, mostly than

