01:36:15.784 --> 01:36:19.704
And so again, I think this is now moving into the clinic,

1630
01:36:19.984 --> 01:36:23.664
but one of the things that we really have to do is to understand is this one

1631
01:36:23.724 --> 01:36:27.124
condition or is this several conditions that converge on the

1632
01:36:27.184 --> 01:36:31.074
same terminal appearance? And

1633
01:36:31.124 --> 01:36:34.644
then how can we parse those conditions out into understanding molecular mechanisms

1634
01:36:34.684 --> 01:36:35.424
