01:37:55.691 --> 01:37:58.412
equations, and how can that be moved into the clinic?

1658
01:37:58.811 --> 01:38:02.631
And one thing that is very interesting for people to think about, many

1659
01:38:03.072 --> 01:38:06.891
clinicians, endocrinologists, cardiologists, respiratory physicians,

1660
01:38:07.971 --> 01:38:11.692
challenge the organism, in other words, the patient, when they try to make

1661
01:38:11.771 --> 01:38:15.371
diagnoses and try to understand where the patient is on the

1662
01:38:15.431 --> 01:38:17.291
personal trajectory of disease progression.

1663
01:38:17.571 --> 01:38:20.911
That's standard practice in multiplicities

1664
01:38:21.012 --> 01:38:24.611
