1670
01:38:43.931 --> 01:38:47.431
to the second degree to

1671
01:38:47.531 --> 01:38:51.091
characterize the organism. And so one of the things that this model

1672
01:38:51.152 --> 01:38:55.051
suggests is that if safely done, you can potentially learn something about the

1673
01:38:55.131 --> 01:38:58.951
patient and their personal trajectory through perturbation response.

1674
01:38:59.171 --> 01:38:59.832
Does that make sense?

1675
01:39:00.571 --> 01:39:01.491
Yeah. Thank you.

